Author: coinnup
Title: ğŸ”¥ COINNUP - Global Financial Platform ğŸ”¥
Body: Hello everybody,  We have some GOOD NEWS for all of those who's been waiting. The Coinnup ICO website is up and running!  You can check it out here   ico.coinnup.com  If you want to learn more Blockchain Powered FinTech and e-Commerce Platform,  you can SIGN UP for an early access.  BIG NEWS - Pre ICO sale will start in 46 days!  The website contains all the information about Coinnup & ICO launch. We are proud of the fact that Coinnup ICO is the first ICO to be launched on its own platform!  Main Features of the website:  - Send and Receive Payments - Buy, Sell or Withdraw - CU Tokens - POS System - One Ultimate Wallet - Global Transactions - Online & Offline Shopping - Fiat Central - Coinnup Card - Borderless Transactions - Instant Transactions - ICO Launchpad - Coin Rankings & Portfolio Management - Coinnup App - The Bounty Program  Check our Whitepaper for all additional information. Also, feel free to ask us any question you may have, or gives a feedback. We love to hear your opinion. You can do that on our Telegram group .  We can't wait to hear your opinion on this! Stay tuned, The Coinnup Team
